The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Nation | Nation Briefs
                                                                                                                 NATION BRIEFS
                                      
	New York, March 8 (AP): An 18-year-old Pakistani man has been convicted of a hate crime after he forcibly cut a Sikh students hair in school.          
	Prosecutors say Umair Ahmed forced the 15-year-old boy to take off his turban and cut his hair at the Newtown High School in Elmhurst in the citys Queens borough. The incident happened last May. Ahmed faces up to four years in prison when he is sentenced next month.                  
	Nagpur (PTI): A Mumbai-bound Indigo aircraft with 140 passengers hit a deer on the runway of the airport here while taking off on Friday night.The flight of the private carrier was unhindered and passengers were safe, but the deer died.                   
	Chennai (PTI): An exclusively women-operated Air India flight left for Colombo to mark International Womens Day. Captain M. Deepa along with an all-women cabin crew, flew to the Sri Lankan capital on Saturday. The women passengers on the flight were received with rose buds to mark the occasion.                  
	Dubai (PTI): An Indian died when a crane collapsed at a construction site in Sharjah on Friday. The victim was moving construction material to the fifth floor when the crane went crashing down, apparently because of overloading or a technical glitch.                  
	Muzaffarnagar (PTI): A case has been registered against a school headmaster for allegedly beating up a Class IV student. The 11-year-old girl fell unconscious and had to be taken to hospital after being thrashed by Anand Pal on Friday.                  
	 Coimbatore (PTI): A tea estate employee in the Kallar forest area has been killed in a bison attack. The body of the 40-year-old superviser was found by forest officials and relatives.
                                                                                                                           
